  "bullets": [
   "Case study using household income transfer data analyzed with quantile regression, comparing figures an LLM computed directly against results from dedicated econometric software.",
   "The paper does not name the model. LLMs were asked to run statistical calculations on raw data, and their coefficients were checked against Stata computations.",
   "LLM-generated regression outputs produced fabricated coefficients that contradicted the Stata results, leading the author to restrict LLMs to research design and code generation rather than final computation."
